INSERT INTO artists VALUES(1,'2 Chainz',3,'https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6761610000f178f556662d187b9191c421be1c','https://open.spotify.com/artist/17lzZA2AlOHwCwFALHttmp','2 Chainz aka Dos Cadenas aka Big Toni!');
INSERT INTO artists VALUES(2,'21 Savage',3,'https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6761610000f178e01decbaa565f3feaaade6a9','https://open.spotify.com/artist/1URnnhqYAYcrqrcwql10ft','An Atlanta-based rapper who kicked off his career with the crew Slaughtergang, MC 21 Savage hit as a solo artist with his 2014 single ''Picky''. First single ''Picky'' launched his solo career in 2014, and his debut mixtape, The Slaughter Tape, dropped in 2015. The Free Guwop EP, with , landed that same year, as did a second solo mixtape, Slaughter King. In 2016 he joined  for the collaborative EP Savage Mode, which climbed into the Top 25 of the Billboard 200 and peaked at number seven on the Rap Albums chart. Savage''s debut full-length arrived in the summer of 2017. Issa Album (/) featured production by , , , and , as well as an appearance by  on ''Whole Lot''.');
INSERT INTO artists VALUES(3,'5 Seconds of Summer',1,'https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6761610000f17892ce1e218cb7b48386efe3d8','https://open.spotify.com/artist/5Rl15oVamLq7FbSb0NNBNy','Your favorite boyband.');
INSERT INTO artists VALUES(4,'6ix9ine',3,'https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6761610000f1780f9be189941db077530d5ae0','https://open.spotify.com/artist/7gZfnEnfiaHzxARJ2LeXrf','N/A');
INSERT INTO artists VALUES(5,'A Boogie Wit da Hoodie',3,'https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6761610000f1787f69a00b3dacd4d959859dce','https://open.spotify.com/artist/31W5EY0aAly4Qieq6OFu6I','Nonchalant flows, memorable hooks, trap beats that make plenty of room for melody, and the occasional hint of R&B smoothness all combine into an effortless style for Bronx rapper A Boogie wit da Hoodie. The rapper hit the scene in 2016, releasing his debut mixtape, Artist, on his own label, but later signing with . He scored big with the triple-platinum single ''Drowning'' in 2017, which led to the Top Ten hit The Bigger Artist and its chart-topping 2018 follow-up, Hoodie SZN. Boogie continued his commercial hot streak with projects like 2020''s Artist 2.0 and the 2024 studio album Better Off Alone.');
INSERT INTO artists VALUES(7,'AJR',4,'https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6761610000f178d0f8fb5691ea660889d10eb1','https://open.spotify.com/artist/6s22t5Y3prQHyaHWUN1R1C','Re-envisioning what pop can be in the 21st century, AJR unassumingly emerged as a ubiquitous hit-making outlier and one of the biggest indie bands in the world. Since 2012, the multiplatinum indie pop trio—Adam [bass, vocals], Jack [vocals, guitar], and Ryan [ukulele, piano, vocals]—have generated billions of streams and earned one triple-platinum single, one double-platinum single, four platinum singles, and one platinum album. 2019’s Neotheater marked their biggest first-week debut, bowing at #8 on the Billboard Top 200, #1 on the Top Alternative Albums Chart, and #1 on the Top Rock Albums Chart. Cemented as part of the modern zeitgeist, Spotify touted ''Sober Up''[feat. Rivers Cuomo] among the ''Best Rock Songs of the 2010s,'' while Apple Music included ''Weak'' on its ''Best Alt Songs of the 2010s.'' Not to mention, they remain one of the ''500 Most-Listened to Artists'' on Spotify. On the heels of Neotheater, they dropped the 2020 platinum blockbuster ''BANG!'', which they performed on TODAY, The Ellen DeGeneres Show, and even at the Macy’s Thanksgiving Day Parade and raced up the Alternative and Pop Radio charts. Now, the band has opened up their world like never before on their fourth full-length album, OK ORCHESTRA.');
INSERT INTO artists VALUES(9,'Anne-Marie',3,'https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6761610000f1780f625b6df41bdd56196351bf','https://open.spotify.com/artist/1zNqDE7qDGCsyzJwohVaoX','Anne-Marie’s rise to stardom has been nothing short of meteoric. A former 3 x world karate champion and West End child star turned multi-platinum-selling artist, Anne-Marie has gone onto become one of the world’s most-loved and successful pop stars of our times. Following a string of chart-busting singles over her career to date – from her Ed Sheeran co-write ‘2002’ to this year’s ‘PSYCHO’ – Anne-Marie is an artist who wins on her playful commentary, idiosyncratic storytelling, magnetic vocals and infectious personality, as was perfectly showcased on her 2018 debut album, Speak Your Mind [that years’ biggest-selling debut release in the UK and an album that’s now sold over four million copies, globally]. Making her prime time debut as a new coach on The Voice this year, Anne-Marie is now working on her 3rd album. ');
INSERT INTO artists VALUES(10,'Anuel AA',3,'https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6761610000f178c5c589b667f600c299552ee5','https://open.spotify.com/artist/2R21vXR83lH98kGeO99Y66','Anuel has earned the title of Latin Global Superstar. Because of the success of the song La ocasion, he entered the artistic world. The artist was arrested and sentenced to 30 months in prison in Puerto Rico at the height of his popularity. On the same day as his release from prison in July 2018, Anuel released his album REAL HASTA LA MUERTE, which received overwhelming support from his fans all over the world. The album reached the top of the music charts across all digital platforms. For more than 26 weeks in 2018, Anuel held the title of most viewed musician on YouTube worldwide. He was nominated for and won the Premio Lo Nuestro 2019 for Best New Artist. ');
INSERT INTO artists VALUES(11,'Ariana Grande',3,'https://i.scdn.co/image/b1dfbe843b0b9f54ab2e588f33e7637d2dab065a','https://open.spotify.com/artist/66CXWjxzNUsdJxJ2JdwvnR','With her four-octave vocal acrobatics and iconic image, American singer, songwriter, and actress Ariana Grande has solidified her place as one of the quintessential pop stars of her generation, racking up stacks of awards and chart records in the process. Emerging in the early 2010s with the hit single The Way, Grande was primed to follow in the footsteps of her biggest influences,  and , due in part to her powerhouse vocals. With its  production, her debut, Yours Truly, underscored her debt to ''90s R&B, but Grande quickly incorporated hip-hop and EDM into her sound.');
INSERT INTO artists VALUES(15,'Bad Bunny',3,'https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6761610000f1788ee9a6f54dcbd4bc95126b14','https://open.spotify.com/artist/4q3ewBCX7sLwd24euuV69X','Bad Bunny is a young urban music singer, rapper and producer originally from Puerto Rico. This talented artist has demonstrated his already overwhelming power, influence and demand with completely sold-out concerts all over Europe, Latin America and the U.S.');
INSERT INTO artists VALUES(16,'Bazzi',3,'https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6761610000f17872a8e86c457085e7fdd3453f','https://open.spotify.com/artist/4GvEc3ANtPPjt1ZJllr5Zl','R&B-influenced pop singer/songwriter Bazzi hit the mainstream after finding viral success with his breakthrough single Mine. The track made a slow climb up the charts, peaking just outside the Top Ten on the Hot 100, and appeared on his Top 40 hit debut, COSMIC.');
INSERT INTO artists VALUES(17,'Beyoncé',3,'https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6761610000f17812e3f20d05a8d6cfde988715','https://open.spotify.com/artist/6vWDO969PvNqNYHIOW5v0m','A powerhouse singer, songwriter, producer, and dancer, Beyoncé is a multifaceted global superstar by any measure. The Houstonian rose to fame in the late ''90s as the central member of pop-R&B group . The following decade, she started her ongoing streak of number one solo studio albums with Dangerously in Love (2003), the source of her first number one pop single, the ecstatic Crazy in Love. ');
INSERT INTO artists VALUES(18,'Billie Eilish',3,'https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6761610000f178d8b9980db67272cb4d2c3daf','https://open.spotify.com/artist/6qqNVTkY8uBg9cP3Jd7DAH','Billie Eilish remains one of the biggest stars to emerge in the 21st century. Her third studio album, HIT ME HARD AND SOFT features 10 tracks written and recorded in her hometown of Los Angeles, with her brother and producer FINNEAS. In 2019, her debut album WHEN WE ALL FALL ASLEEP, WHERE DO WE GO? debuted at No. 1 in 18 countries, and was the most streamed album of that year.');
INSERT INTO artists VALUES(19,'blackbear',3,'https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6761610000f1784f7d049994ac00ed885bfbf2','https://open.spotify.com/artist/2cFrymmkijnjDg9SS92EPM','hope my music helps u smile through the pain of the human condition.. or makes u even more sad if ur down bad & cathartic masochism is what your looking for.. im guilty of this personally.');
INSERT INTO artists VALUES(20,'BLACKPINK',1,'https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6761610000f178c9690bc711d04b3d4fd4b87c','https://open.spotify.com/artist/41MozSoPIsD1dJM0CLPjZF','Following a nearly three-year group hiatus, during which each member expanded their musical horizons through solo projects - BLACKPINK returns in full force with their digital single ‘JUMP’, reaffirming their status as global leaders in music');
INSERT INTO artists VALUES(23,'Bruno Mars',3,'https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6761610000f178c36dd9eb55fb0db4911f25dd','https://open.spotify.com/artist/0du5cEVh5yTK9QJze8zA0C','Bruno Mars is a 16x GRAMMY-winning global superstar, singer, songwriter, multi-instrumentalist, producer, and one of the most-streamed artists in the world. Known for his showmanship and chart-toppers, Bruno has set a number of records throughout his career, including becoming the first artist ever to hit 150 million monthly listeners on Spotify.');
INSERT INTO artists VALUES(24,'BTS',1,'https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6761610000f1785704a64f34fe29ff73ab56bb','https://open.spotify.com/artist/3Nrfpe0tUJi4K4DXYWgMUX','Record-breaking South Korean boy band BTS (aka Bangtan Boys) deliver an energetic blend of dance-pop and hip-hop with deeply introspective lyrics that helped them build a devoted global following while also making them one of the most successful Korean exports in the world. Debuting in the early 2010s with their Skool trilogy, they steadily expanded their audience until breaking into the mainstream consciousness with the Love Yourself series.');
INSERT INTO artists VALUES(25,'Calvin Harris',3,'https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6761610000f178578905d5539cff25568dc097','https://open.spotify.com/artist/7CajNmpbOovFoOoasH2HaY','Producer, DJ and songwriter Calvin Harris stands as the figurehead for modern dance music, having broken world records and dominated the charts. He has over 35 billion combined audio and video streams in his career history, making him one of the most viewed artists on YouTube and one of Sony Music''s biggest streaming artists');
INSERT INTO artists VALUES(26,'Camila Cabello',3,'https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6761610000f17874dc5cfab4be58a97ab61d35','https://open.spotify.com/artist/4nDoRrQiYLoBzwC5BhVJzF','Camila Cabello is a diamond-certified, GRAMMY-nominated Cuban-born singer, songwriter, actress, and activist. She has notably emerged as the first Hispanic woman to reach RIAA Diamond status with her Billboard Hot 100 #1 smash Havana [feat. Young Thug]. ');
INSERT INTO artists VALUES(27,'Cardi B',3,'https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6761610000f1788c2332e6c0ed96d144a91b3f','https://open.spotify.com/artist/4kYSro6naA4h99UJvo89HB','Rapper and entertainer Cardi B draws from a seemingly never-ending supply of confidence, charisma, and evisceratingly sharp flows. She broke through in 2017 with her debut commercially released single, Bodak Yellow, topping the Billboard Hot 100 and becoming the first female rapper to do so in nearly two decades.');
INSERT INTO artists VALUES(29,'Charlie Puth',3,'https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6761610000f1784e2e2c78de847c4d9b12d32f','https://open.spotify.com/artist/6VuMaDnrHyPL1p4EHjYLi7','Charlie Puth has proven to be one of the industry’s most consistent hitmakers and sought-after collaborators. Puth has amassed eight multi-platinum singles, four GRAMMY nominations, three Billboard Music Awards, a Critic’s Choice Award, and a Golden Globe nomination. ');
INSERT INTO artists VALUES(30,'Cheat Codes',4,'https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6761610000f178e76d3aeb58344c63fcc97682','https://open.spotify.com/artist/7DMveApC7UnC2NPfPvlHSU','Los Angeles-based electronic trio Cheat Codes debuted in 2015 with their single Visions, a floor-filling, radio-ready bite of house. Each of the group''s three members -- Kevin Ford, Trevor Dahl, Matthew Russell -- has deep roots in L.A., working on individual projects before joining forces for Cheat Codes. Their different backgrounds helped inform Cheat Codes'' stylistically varied sound, which can range from warm pop to outright big house bangers. ');
INSERT INTO artists VALUES(31,'Childish Gambino',3,'https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6761610000f1783ef779aa0d271adb2b6a3ded','https://open.spotify.com/artist/73sIBHcqh3Z3NyqHKZ7FOL','nobody gives a fu*k');
INSERT INTO artists VALUES(33,'Clean Bandit',1,'https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6761610000f1787a487027eb0c10af725d5410','https://open.spotify.com/artist/6MDME20pz9RveH9rEXvrOM','British dance group Clean Bandit found crossover success by weaving classical music with dance-pop for a beat-driven yet refined sound -- often delivered with high-profile guest vocalists.');
INSERT INTO artists VALUES(34,'Dan + Shay',2,'https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6761610000f1781e6f4e64dc26772155d61ce2','https://open.spotify.com/artist/7z5WFjZAIYejWy0NI5lv4T','3x GRAMMY-winning duo Dan + Shay continue to etch a permanent mark on country music – and beyond – with the release of the duos highly anticipated fifth studio album, Bigger Houses, co-produced by the band’s Dan Smyers and Scott Hendricks.');
INSERT INTO artists VALUES(35,'Daya',3,'https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6761610000f1785ce25fd2eab762a8cee5d200','https://open.spotify.com/artist/6Dd3NScHWwnW6obMFbl1BH','Daya writes songs you can see yourself in. The Diamond-certified GRAMMY Award-winning pop singer and songwriter tunes into pure emotion, channeling her unfiltered feelings in the form of alternately anthemic and intimate genre-breaking bangers. She has not only evolved artistically, but she’s also personally grown up in real-time via nearly a decade of releases. ');
INSERT INTO artists VALUES(36,'Demi Lovato',3,'https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6761610000f1786659b1cb61936bd7bcb229a2','https://open.spotify.com/artist/6S2OmqARrzebs0tKUEyXyp','Demi Lovato is a GRAMMY-nominated and award-winning musician, actor, advocate, and New York Times best-selling author. With an audience of over 240 million on social media, Demi has established herself as a global sensation. With nearly 30 billion streams earned worldwide, Demi has captivated audiences with her renowned powerhouse vocals and illustrious songwriting. ');
INSERT INTO artists VALUES(38,'DJ Khaled',3,'https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6761610000f17833509c0d518064344545f35c','https://open.spotify.com/artist/0QHgL1lAIqAw0HtD7YldmP','No overnight success, DJ Khaled toiled as a disc jockey for years before he became an immensely successful, larger-than-life figure in rap music. Since the latter half of the 2000s, Khaled has factored into triumphant crossover singles that have seemed like events, charming fans with his fun-loving spirit, ebullient interjections, and well-placed talent that has flanked him.');
INSERT INTO artists VALUES(39,'DJ Snake',3,'https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6761610000f178f2855e25f1d9c8a20bcc85ae','https://open.spotify.com/artist/540vIaP2JwjQb9dm3aArA4','Over the last decade, DJ Snake has achieved the kind of rarefied and wildly transformative success that few artists ever come close to attaining. Originally from a housing project on the outskirts of Paris, the multi-platinum-selling DJ/producer has shattered industry records.');
INSERT INTO artists VALUES(40,'DNCE',1,'https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6761610000f178f516ed43c65fe21e21a7c5bd','https://open.spotify.com/artist/6T5tfhQCknKG4UnH90qGnz','Exuberant dance-rock group DNCE broke into the mainstream in 2015 with the EP SWAAY and the single Cake by the Ocean, a multi-platinum international hit that helped propel their 2016 self-titled debut LP into the U.S. Top 20. ');
INSERT INTO artists VALUES(41,'Doja Cat',3,'https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6761610000f178727a2ac15afe659be999beba','https://open.spotify.com/artist/5cj0lLjcoR7YOSnhnX0Po5','Born and raised in L.A., Doja Cat made her first upload to Soundcloud in 2013 at just 16-years-old. She developed a knack for music by studying piano and dance as a kid and listening to the likes of Busta Rhymes, Erykah Badu, Nicki Minaj, Drake, and more.');
INSERT INTO artists VALUES(42,'Drake',3,'https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6761610000f1784293385d324db8558179afd9','https://open.spotify.com/artist/3TVXtAsR1Inumwj472S9r4','Canadian rapper and vocalist Drake has retained a bigger-than-life commercial presence shortly after he hit the scene in 2006, whether with his own chart-topping releases or with a long string of guest appearances.');
INSERT INTO artists VALUES(43,'Dua Lipa',3,'https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6761610000f178d42a27db3286b58553da8858','https://open.spotify.com/artist/6M2wZ9GZgrQXHCFfjv46we','Dua’s eponymous 2017 debut album is certified platinum, spawned six platinum tracks, and made her the first female artist in BRIT Awards history to pick up five nominations in a single year. Dua has 10 GRAMMY nominations with three wins. Globally, she has amassed over 40 billion streams across platforms and has the top two most streamed albums by a female artist of all time on Spotify');
INSERT INTO artists VALUES(44,'Ed Sheeran',3,'https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6761610000f1789e690225ad4445530612ccc9','https://open.spotify.com/artist/6eUKZXaKkcviH0Ku9w2n3V','Idiosyncratic pop singer Ed Sheeran borrows from any style that crosses his path, molding genres to fit a musical character all his own that''s charming, personable, and popular on a global scale. Elements of folk, hip-hop, pop, dance, soul, and rock can be heard in his big hits which gives him a broad appeal among different demographics. ');
INSERT INTO artists VALUES(45,'Ella Mai',3,'https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6761610000f178173a42b51755d3075d67831c','https://open.spotify.com/artist/7HkdQ0gt53LP4zmHsL0nap','Raised in southwest London, Ella Mai Howell moved to New York at the age of 12, then returned to England after she graduated from high school.');
INSERT INTO artists VALUES(48,'Fifth Harmony',1,'https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6761610000f1785acb3cb0a8b87d3952738b97','https://open.spotify.com/artist/1l8Fu6IkuTP0U5QetQJ5Xt','Multi-platinum selling group Fifth Harmony’s third album Fifth Harmony, via Syco/Epic Records, blasted to the top of the charts around the world upon its August 25 release. The album was the #1 pop and second-best overall selling album in the U.S., debuted at #4 on the U.S. Billboard Top 200 chart and peaked at #1 on iTunes in more than 50 countries');
INSERT INTO artists VALUES(51,'Florida Georgia Line',2,'https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6761610000f178aa2d9bd207a62adc3edf6631','https://open.spotify.com/artist/3b8QkneNDz4JHKKKlLgYZg','Florida Georgia Line came out of nowhere in 2012 to become the biggest country group of the new decade. The vehicle of their success was Cruise, a slick, shimmering ode to the wide-open road that became an unkillable crossover hit in 2013 and, eventually, the biggest country single of all time.');
INSERT INTO artists VALUES(52,'Future',3,'https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6761610000f17824e41f491b129093a6fee383','https://open.spotify.com/artist/1RyvyyTE3xzB2ZywiAwp0i','Chart-topping and influential rapper Future is known for a uniquely fluid and melodic yet mumbling vocal style. He busted out of the South at the dawn of the 2010s with a flurry of mixtapes, high-charting albums, certified platinum singles, and contributions to several other hits as a featured artist, then continued to hover at the top of his game, both commercially and creatively, in the years that followed.');
INSERT INTO artists VALUES(53,'Galantis',2,'https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6761610000f1782ca90cb37bf1557d385b9d48','https://open.spotify.com/artist/4sTQVOfp9vEMCemLw50sbu','Galantis is the dance music project of Christian Karlsson (aka Bloodshy). RIAA gold-certified debut album Pharmacy reached No. 1 on the Billboard Dance album chart on the strength of platinum-certified single “Peanut Butter Jelly” and 3x platinum certified smash “Runaway (U & I)”');
INSERT INTO artists VALUES(55,'G-Eazy',3,'https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6761610000f178e818f7ca0d47f038a9aa246a','https://open.spotify.com/artist/02kJSzxNuaWGqwubyUba0Z','With his slicked-back hair and leather jacket, G-Eazy was known as ''the James Dean of rap'' when he debuted in the late 2000s. Armed with bars that detailed hedonistic excess and conflicted inner turmoil, he steadily climbed the charts in the 2010s');
INSERT INTO artists VALUES(56,'George Ezra',3,'https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6761610000f178be936a26ceb9cbbdec7df15b','https://open.spotify.com/artist/2ysnwxxNtSgbb9t1m2Ur4j','After two blockbuster albums – Wanted On Voyage (2014) and Staying At Tamara’s (2018), both of which reached number 1 in the UK and sold millions around the world, and the latter of which earned him his first number 1 single in ‘Shotgun’ and won him the 2019 Brit Award for British Male Solo Artist – it was time to return to heart and hearth, with an album written and produced entirely in London with longstanding collaborator Joel Pott.');
INSERT INTO artists VALUES(57,'Hailee Steinfeld',3,'https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6761610000f178a961383967f3a3a54e794a15','https://open.spotify.com/artist/5p7f24Rk5HkUZsaS3BLG5F','Academy Award nominated actress and Republic Records multi-platinum recording artist Hailee Steinfeld remains a force to be reckoned with in pop music');
INSERT INTO artists VALUES(58,'Halsey',3,'https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6761610000f178d707e1c5177614c4ec95a06c','https://open.spotify.com/artist/26VFTg2z8YR0cCuwLzESi2','Diamond-certified and GRAMMY Award-nominated, Halsey has amassed 50+ billion streams, 75M RIAA-certified singles, and four RIAA-certified albums. In 2024, their latest album The Great Impersonator debuted at No. 1 on Billboard’s Top Rock & Alternative and Top Alternative Albums charts, continuing a streak of No. 1 debuts that includes If I Can’t Have Love, I Want Power (2021), Hopeless Fountain Kingdom (2017), and Badlands (2015). Badlands remains one of the only albums ever with every track certified Gold, Platinum, or Multi-Platinum.');
INSERT INTO artists VALUES(59,'iann dior',3,'https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6761610000f1782aeeeb3db9b941db74d2cfe2','https://open.spotify.com/artist/6ASri4ePR7RlsvIQgWPJpS','Iann Dior is a multi-platinum recording artist and musician who has established himself as a cultural force in both music and fashion. With over 3.7 billion streams to date, Iann broke onto the scene with his 7x Platinum Billboard Hot 100 #1 hit “Mood” featuring 24kGoldn, which alone has been streamed over 2 billion times and was recently named one of Billboard’s Top 100 Songs of the Century, landing at #23. ');
INSERT INTO artists VALUES(60,'Imagine Dragons',1,'https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6761610000f178920dc1f617550de8388f368e','https://open.spotify.com/artist/53XhwfbYqKCa1cC15pYq2q','Imagine Dragons continue to redefine rock in the 21st century. Filling stadiums, crafting cloud-rattling anthems, & breaking records at every turn, diamond-certified GRAMMY Award-winning band Imagine Dragons occupy rarified air as one of the biggest rock bands in the world.');
INSERT INTO artists VALUES(61,'James Arthur',3,'https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6761610000f1786867a4ce52401bd378bb5179','https://open.spotify.com/artist/4IWBUUAFIplrNtaOHcJPRM','James Arthur can look back on a decade-long career, including 4 studio albums to date, 16 billion sold units (audio/video streams/downloads), and countless sold-out gigs at some of the most legendary venues across the globe.');
INSERT INTO artists VALUES(65,'Jonas Blue',3,'https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6761610000f178f79f4c1f658cfcb74baeae51','https://open.spotify.com/artist/1HBjj22wzbscIZ9sEb5dyf','Jonas Blue’s career to date has been astounding and its effect has been felt worldwide with singles like ‘Fast Car’, ‘Perfect Strangers’ ‘Rise, ‘Mama’ & ‘Polaroid’ collectively having been certified platinum over 130 times around the globe. Amassing an army of recognisable hits, with over 22 billion global streams, 92 million worldwide singles sales, 6 billion video views, BRIT Billion Award Holder, BRIT certified Breakthrough Album, 5 BRIT Award nominations and multiple brand deals, Jonas has cemented his name as a main stage DJ and pop powerhouse.');
INSERT INTO artists VALUES(66,'Jonas Brothers',1,'https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6761610000f178142120beb4014a7f8abd0cf0','https://open.spotify.com/artist/7gOdHgIoIKoe4i9Tta6qdD','Standing out as one of the most successful groups of the 21st century, Jonas Brothers—Nick Jonas, Joe Jonas, and Kevin Jonas—have sold north of 20 million albums and counting, garnered two GRAMMY Award nominations, earned 26 Billboard Hot 100 hits, logged three consecutive #1 debuts on the Billboard 200, and generated billions of streams. Among many accolades, they’ve recently claimed a star on the Hollywood Walk of Fame. ');
INSERT INTO artists VALUES(67,'Juice WRLD',3,'https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6761610000f1781908e1a8b79abf71d5598944','https://open.spotify.com/artist/4MCBfE4596Uoi2O4DtmEMz','Juice WRLD became a Top Ten hitmaker delivering introspective lyrics atop melodic production. His heartsick 2018 debut Goodbye & Good Riddance (2018), home to his biggest hit Lucid Dreams, reflected a wide range of stylistic influences: R&B instrumentation, dreamy beats, and even indie rock melodicism. ');
INSERT INTO artists VALUES(68,'Justin Timberlake',3,'https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6761610000f1789d3f9efc8e0030306e583cef','https://open.spotify.com/artist/31TPClRtHm23RisEBtV3X7','Justin Timberlake is one of the most recognizable pop stars of his generation, jumping from platform to platform on his way to establishing himself as something bigger than a star: he is a self-sustained empire. Timberlake began his rise on television, performing on The New Mickey Mouse Club as a child in the ''90s, but he earned his superstardom as one of the frontmen for *NSYNC, one of the most popular boy bands at the turn of the millennium. ');
INSERT INTO artists VALUES(70,'Kendrick Lamar',3,'https://i.scdn.co/image/3a836196bfb341f736c7fe2704fb75de53f8dfbb','https://open.spotify.com/artist/2YZyLoL8N0Wb9xBt1NhZWg','One of the most acclaimed artists of his generation, hip-hop or otherwise, Kendrick Lamar is known for his top-tier lyricism, virtuosic microphone command, and sharp conceptual vision. His talents have translated to a rare combination of continuous chart feats and critical acclaim, plus respect and support from the rappers who paved the way for his advancement.');
INSERT INTO artists VALUES(71,'Khalid',3,'https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6761610000f17831072db9da0311ecfabe96bf','https://open.spotify.com/artist/6LuN9FCkKOj5PcnpouEgny','Khalid is a nontraditional R&B singer and songwriter with a large following attracted to his undemonstrative but heartfelt vocal style and down-to-earth perspective. ');
INSERT INTO artists VALUES(74,'Lady Gaga',3,'https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6761610000f178c8d3d98a1bccbe71393dbfbf','https://open.spotify.com/artist/1HY2Jd0NmPuamShAr6KMms','Academy Award and 14-time GRAMMY-winner Lady Gaga is a one-of-a-kind artist and performer. She has amassed an outstanding 110 million global album sales, 175 billion streams, and 758 million song consumption units, making her one of the best-selling musicians of all time. Her most recent pop album, Chromatica, became her sixth consecutive #1 on the Billboard 200 chart, making her the first female artist to achieve this over a ten-year period (2011-2020)');
INSERT INTO artists VALUES(75,'Lana Del Rey',3,'https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6761610000f178b99cacf8acd5378206767261','https://open.spotify.com/artist/00FQb4jTyendYWaN8pK0wa','N/A');
INSERT INTO artists VALUES(77,'Lauv',3,'https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6761610000f1785af53f295e6c42529fbd0873','https://open.spotify.com/artist/5JZ7CnR6gTvEMKX4g70Amv','A truly groundbreaking force in today’s music world, Lauv embodies both the immense freedom of an independent artist and the hitmaking power of a pop phenomenon');
INSERT INTO artists VALUES(78,'Lewis Capaldi',3,'https://i.scdn.co/image/5ed13d249e562fea4e296aaeb745ce06d27ec88f','https://open.spotify.com/artist/4GNC7GD6oZMSxPGyXy4MNB','With two record-breaking albums, billions of streams, and headline tours across five continents, his rise from small-town Scottish pubs to global arenas has captured hearts worldwide.');
INSERT INTO artists VALUES(80,'Lil Baby',3,'https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6761610000f1786cad3eff5adc29e20f189a6c','https://open.spotify.com/artist/5f7VJjfbwm532GiveGC0ZK','Some artists define a genre, but Lil Baby defines a generation. The GRAMMY Award-winning rapper has smashed records, made history, and impacted the course of modern hip-hop with his instantly identifiable and inimitable style. He has garnered dozens of multi platinum certifications and tens of billions of streams as arguably the biggest new rapper to emerge this decade. ');
INSERT INTO artists VALUES(81,'Lil Nas X',3,'https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6761610000f178d66f1e0c883f319443d68c45','https://open.spotify.com/artist/7jVv8c5Fj3E9VhNjxT4snq','you in dreamworld and u listening to dreamboy');
INSERT INTO artists VALUES(82,'Lil Peep',3,'https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6761610000f1786685f03de475c4efb27da3c4','https://open.spotify.com/artist/2kCcBybjl3SAtIcwdWpUe3','An icon of the SoundCloud rap era that dominated the mid- to late 2010s, Lil Peep connected with his fans through both his genre-bending style and his lyrics, which vulnerably and transparently addressed issues of depression, addiction, and anxiety. A run of strong mixtapes and guest appearances generated media buzz around the rapper, his approach to life, and his music, which polarized both listeners and the press.');
INSERT INTO artists VALUES(83,'Lil Pump',3,'https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6761610000f178726e109c49131b6ed60ae8a0','https://open.spotify.com/artist/3wyVrVrFCkukjdVIdirGVY','Lil Pump, whose real name is Gazzy García, is an American rapper and songwriter born on August 17, 2000, in Miami, Florida. He gained fame in 2017 with his breakout single Gucci Gang, which peaked at number three on the Billboard Hot 100 and was certified five-times platinum by the RIAA. Known for his energetic and rebellious style, Lil Pump is a prominent figure in the SoundCloud rap movement, characterized by its lo-fi production and internet-based promotion.');
INSERT INTO artists VALUES(85,'Lil Uzi Vert',3,'https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6761610000f17830122c0d3ead72f96bb5ee93','https://open.spotify.com/artist/4O15NlyKLIASxsJ0PrXPfz','Over the course of their illustrious career, the multiple GRAMMY-nominated and RIAA Diamond-certified superstar has amassed over 31 billion career streams, cementing their status as a global icon.');
INSERT INTO artists VALUES(86,'Lil Wayne',3,'https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6761610000f178c63aded6f4bf4d06d1377106','https://open.spotify.com/artist/55Aa2cqylxrFIXC767Z865','Lil Wayne began his career as a near novelty, a preteen delivering hardcore Southern hip-hop. Through years of maturation and prolific output, during which the delivery of his humorous and wordplay-heavy rhymes gradually changed from ringing and pugnacious to stoned and rasped, he developed into a million-unit-selling artist with a massive body of work, one so inventive and cunning that it makes his claim of being the best rapper alive" worth considering."');
INSERT INTO artists VALUES(87,'Little Mix',1,'https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6761610000f17808cd53940cbf5813ee5fe565','https://open.spotify.com/artist/3e7awlrlDSwF3iM0WBjGMp','Perrie Edwards, Leigh-Anne Pinnock and Jade Thirlwall have established themselves as the world’s biggest girl band - they have sold over 50 million records worldwide, collected over 17 million Spotify listeners, received over 3 billion Youtube views, and collated 12 billion streams worldwide');
INSERT INTO artists VALUES(88,'Lizzo',3,'https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6761610000f1780d66b3670294bf801847dae2','https://open.spotify.com/artist/56oDRnqbIiwx4mymNEv7dS','There’s nobody like Lizzo. The 4x GRAMMY Award-winning, Emmy-Award-winning superstar singer, songwriter, rapper, and actress has left an indelible and incomparable mark on popular culture. She has garnered numerous accolades, notched 2 Hot 100 #1 smashes, earned dozens of gold, platinum, and multiplatinum certifications, packed arenas worldwide, and shined in blockbuster films.');
INSERT INTO artists VALUES(90,'Lorde',3,'https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6761610000f178c4902f080d3620b3e6da80c3','https://open.spotify.com/artist/163tK9Wjr9P9DmM0AVK7lm','The magic lives close to the edge');
INSERT INTO artists VALUES(95,'Macklemore',3,'https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6761610000f178488b3b242f97163a7f8e17b9','https://open.spotify.com/artist/3JhNCzhSMTxs9WLGJJxWOY','Multi-platinum and diamond selling GRAMMY® award winning artist Macklemore has made history with a combination of commercial success, critical acclaim, and international appeal. With a total of 13.2 BILLION COMBINED STREAMS to date, Macklemore is one of the most successful independent artists of all time. Macklemore has recently released two new singles as part of a new album campaign, set for release in 2023.');
INSERT INTO artists VALUES(100,'Mark Ronson',3,'https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6761610000f178105cc9628c315b29d299fbb4','https://open.spotify.com/artist/3hv9jJF3adDNsBSIQDqcjp','Grounded in hip-hop yet never averse to pop, Mark Ronson has applied his voracious musical obsessions to become one of the most commercially successful producers from the mid-2000s onward.');
INSERT INTO artists VALUES(101,'Maroon 5',1,'https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6761610000f178288ac05481cedc5bddb5b11b','https://open.spotify.com/artist/04gDigrS5kc9YWfZHwBETP','Maroon 5 -- and, specifically, its frontman  -- became the face of blue-eyed soul in the 21st century, managing to navigate shifting trends in music and fashion to be one of the biggest pop bands of their generation. They took the long way to the top, evolving from the straight-ahead ''90s rock band  into the sleek, soulful Maroon 5 with 2002''s Songs About Jane, an album that languished for two years until This Love climbed to number five on Billboard''s Hot 100 in 2004.');
INSERT INTO artists VALUES(102,'Marshmello',3,'https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6761610000f17841e4a3b8c1d45a9e49b6de21','https://open.spotify.com/artist/64KEffDW9EtZ1y2vBYgq8T','GRAMMY-nominated Marshmello''s star continues to rise as the famously masked artist breaks boundaries across the industry. With chart-topping singles and collaborations with the likes of Juice WRLD, Halsey, Demi Lovato, Bastille, Kane Brown, Selena Gomez, Khalid, Jonas Brothers, and more, Marshmello has clocked a staggering 13 billion streams across Spotify alone');
INSERT INTO artists VALUES(103,'Martin Garrix',3,'https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6761610000f17866d17ee8690d2e8d94ee7387','https://open.spotify.com/artist/60d24wfXkVzDSfLS6hyCjZ','Martin Garrix - the name that belongs to one of the youngest and most successful DJ’s/producers championing the pop and electronic scene. Garrix has taken his expertise across the globe, by headlining festivals, breaking through territories, and collaborating with major stars including Dua Lipa, Khalid and Bono, and The Edge. Climbing yet another rung of his ladder to stardom, he is a founder of his very own label (STMPD RCRDS), owner of a studio complex in Amsterdam, and a mentor to upcoming artists.');
INSERT INTO artists VALUES(107,'Migos',4,'https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6761610000f178f4593f7b778219838d858c34','https://open.spotify.com/artist/6oMuImdp5ZcFhWP0ESe6mG','While their rise to fame was somewhere between fast and meteoric, the Atlanta trio Migos are steeped in the Southern tradition of hip-hop groups. Members are all related, grew up together and first started making music in 2009 under the name Polo Club, with the name Migos becoming official in 2010.');
INSERT INTO artists VALUES(110,'Miley Cyrus',3,'https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6761610000f1787e8110a92ec2252f0821f8b8','https://open.spotify.com/artist/5YGY8feqx7naU7z4HrwZM6','Miley Cyrus has captivated generations, from shaping childhoods as Hannah Montana to smashing walls with “Wrecking Ball.” Miley’s music career is unique, constantly experimenting with new sounds and known as a chameleon across genres.');
INSERT INTO artists VALUES(122,'OneRepublic',1,'https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6761610000f17877bf00f67e21f514dc44c485','https://open.spotify.com/artist/5Pwc4xIPtQLFEnJriah9YJ','GRAMMY nominated OneRepublic is comprised of singer/songwriter and lead vocalist Ryan Tedder, guitarists Zach Filkins and Drew Brown, keys Brian Willett, bassist and cellist Brent Kutzle, and drummer Eddie Fisher. ');
INSERT INTO artists VALUES(123,'Ozuna',3,'https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6761610000f17839ce949d62ff47fc1de1a2d9','https://open.spotify.com/artist/1i8SpTcr7yvPOmcqrbnVXY','Juan Carlos Ozuna Rosado, professionally known as Ozuna, is a record-setting, award-winning reggaeton singer and songwriter from Puerto Rico. He writes positive, uplifting songs that encourage people to work toward their dreams while avoiding the use of profanity out of respect for his daughter. ');
INSERT INTO artists VALUES(126,'Playboi Carti',3,'https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6761610000f178504ff11d788162fbf8078654','https://open.spotify.com/artist/699OTQXzgjhIYAHMy9RyPD','In just a few short years, rapper Playboi Carti has amassed over 19B streams worldwide. Carti has been unstoppable since the release of his 2017 single “Magnolia,” as its meteoric rise garnered cosigns from Beyoncé and features on series like Atlanta.');
INSERT INTO artists VALUES(127,'Polo G',3,'https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6761610000f178dec41838906c58af1c29c9da','https://open.spotify.com/artist/6AgTAQt8XS6jRWi4sX7w49','Polo G is a versatile rapper who has achieved several multi-platinum albums and singles. He spent time in Chicago''s correctional facilities before getting a major-label contract and viral hits. Still in his late teens, the rapper left jail and began releasing tracks and videos while still unsigned and without management. ');
INSERT INTO artists VALUES(129,'Post Malone',3,'https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6761610000f178b894ef9fa437b0389c5567cc','https://open.spotify.com/artist/246dkjvS1zLTtiykXe5h60','Diamond-certified American hitmaker Post Malone bridges the gap between the worlds of rap and the pop mainstream. Within five years of his debut, he went from underground genre novelty to certified superstar, amassing a string of Top Ten singles with a hybrid style that combined his unique vocal delivery, pained lyrics, and hip-hop production inspired as much by Tim McGraw as Kanye West.');
INSERT INTO artists VALUES(130,'Rae Sremmurd',2,'https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6761610000f178209b540fb909a4e61c3ffa01','https://open.spotify.com/artist/7iZtZyCzp3LItcw1wtPI3D','Rae Sremmurd specialize in rambunctious trap-based anthems that have topped the pop charts and earned platinum certifications. Atlanta-based brothers  and  debuted in 2013 with the lashing party track We heard on producer ''s Mike Will Been Trill mixtape, and truly took off two years later with the chart-topping SremmLife, their official debut, featuring No Flex Zone and No Type among its five multi-platinum singles.');
INSERT INTO artists VALUES(133,'Rihanna',3,'https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6761610000f17899e4fca7c0b7cb166d915789','https://open.spotify.com/artist/5pKCCKE2ajJHZ9KAiaK11H','Rihanna is an Academy Award nominated and Grammy winning artist, philanthropist, and businesswoman, recognized as one of the best-selling recording artists of all time. She holds the record for the most Diamond-certified RIAA singles by any female artist. All of her studio albums have achieved Platinum or Multi-Platinum status, including Good Girl Gone Bad, Loud, and Anti, cementing her legacy as a music industry legend. Beyond her musical achievements, Rihanna is celebrated for her humanitarian involvement, entrepreneurship, and fashion industry influence.');
INSERT INTO artists VALUES(134,'Sam Feldt',3,'https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6761610000f1789b494e739143983605696170','https://open.spotify.com/artist/20gsENnposVs2I4rQ5kvrf','Since bursting onto the scene with his multi-platinum-selling remix of Show Me Love, Sam has continued redefining dance music''s boundaries. His signature style—a blend of deep house with pop sensibilities—has earned him a dedicated fan base and critical acclaim. ');
INSERT INTO artists VALUES(135,'Sam Smith',3,'https://i.scdn.co/image/f9c59fff374544fb32293622bd8fce042c2756b4','https://open.spotify.com/artist/2wY79sveU1sp5g7SokKOiI','Multi-Platinum, GRAMMY, BRIT, Golden Globe and Academy Award winning artist Sam Smith is one of the most celebrated musical artists to emerge in recent history. Their most recent album is Sam’s 4th studio and 3rd #1 album, building on the success of critically acclaimed 2020 predecessor.');
INSERT INTO artists VALUES(136,'Saweetie',3,'https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6761610000f17808508fea5d4e92cf4d221834','https://open.spotify.com/artist/6cK3NBO6uP7hh0oyuVELFl','As a dynamic powerhouse, Saweetie continues to solidify herself as a multifaceted artist with her chart-topping songs, successful collaborations, philanthropic endeavors, and captivating on-screen performances. ');
INSERT INTO artists VALUES(139,'Sean Paul',3,'https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6761610000f17860c3e9abe7327c0097738f22','https://open.spotify.com/artist/3Isy6kedDrgPYoTS1dazA9','Jamaican dancehall singer and rapper Sean Paul broke into the global mainstream in the early 2000s with pop-friendly party jams like Get Busy from his Grammy-winning Dutty Rock album, plus the chart-topping smash Temperature.');
INSERT INTO artists VALUES(141,'Selena Gomez',3,'https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6761610000f178a5205abffd84341e5bace828','https://open.spotify.com/artist/0C8ZW7ezQVs4URX5aX7Kqx','Selena Gomez is a multi-talented performer with featured roles on the screen both small and large, and a musical career that reached the summit of the charts from its very beginning and stayed planted there for many years. ');
INSERT INTO artists VALUES(142,'Shawn Mendes',3,'https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6761610000f17846e7a06fa6dfefaed6a3f0db','https://open.spotify.com/artist/7n2wHs1TKAczGzO7Dd2rGr','GRAMMY-nominated & multi-platinum singer/songwriter Shawn Mendes has released 4 acclaimed studio albums, with his 5th studio album Shawn out now. The new album draws deeply from his travels and experiences over the last few years, following the cancellation of his 2022 tour. ');
INSERT INTO artists VALUES(146,'Steve Aoki',3,'https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6761610000f1787c4240b7951da248f3404e42','https://open.spotify.com/artist/77AiFEVeAVj2ORpC85QVJs','2x-GRAMMY-Nominated artist/DJ/producer Steve Aoki is a true visionary. His career boasts a lauded cross-genre discography that includes 9 studio albums and collaborations with Lil Uzi Vert, Maluma, Ne-Yo, BTS, Linkin Park and Louis Tomlinson amongst others. A true renaissance man, Steve Aoki is also a fashion designer, author and entrepreneur.');
INSERT INTO artists VALUES(147,'Stormzy',3,'https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6761610000f178a66d3bfba2c1f0b4a0b278e5','https://open.spotify.com/artist/2SrSdSvpminqmStGELCSNd','A London-based MC of Ghanaian heritage known for his spirited blend of grime, gospel, and R&B, Stormzy is one of the U.K.''s most successful artists, with a trio of chart-topping, widely acclaimed albums to his name. Climbing out of the underground grime scene with a series of triumphant mixtapes, singles, and freestyles, he made his breakthrough in 2017 with his platinum-certified debut album, Gang Signs & Prayer. ');
INSERT INTO artists VALUES(149,'Taylor Swift',3,'https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6761610000f1785a00969a4698c3132a15fbb0','https://open.spotify.com/artist/06HL4z0CvFAxyc27GXpf02','And, baby, that’s show business for you. ');
INSERT INTO artists VALUES(150,'The 1975',1,'https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6761610000f17889348336354096fd4e36ca73','https://open.spotify.com/artist/3mIj9lX2MWuHmhNCA7LSCW','Your new era. Your old friends. The 1975. ');
INSERT INTO artists VALUES(151,'The Chainsmokers',2,'https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6761610000f1783c02f4fb4cc9187c488afd50','https://open.spotify.com/artist/69GGBxA162lTqCwzJG5jLp','Grammy Award-winning and Billboard Chart topping artist/producer duo, The Chainsmokers, have evolved into a dominating musical force with a diverse repertoire of songs that have led them to become one of music’s hottest recording artists.');
INSERT INTO artists VALUES(152,'The Lumineers',1,'https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6761610000f178c79f78fd72a3e5faf699a8be','https://open.spotify.com/artist/16oZKvXb6WkQlVAjwo2Wbg','The Lumineers are one of the world’s most beloved bands with 24 #1 hits. The band has become a touring juggernaut, selling out arenas throughout the world. “Ho Hey” was their first hit single from their self-titled debut. ');
INSERT INTO artists VALUES(153,'The Vamps',2,'https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6761610000f17877ef80571a40d9d19cf52208','https://open.spotify.com/artist/7gAppWoH7pcYmphCVTXkzs','The Vamps, aka Brad Simpson, Connor Ball, Tristan Evans and James McVey, had never really had the chance to take time before the pandemic struck. Since their platinum-selling debut album, Meet The Vamps, crashed into the UK charts at number ');
INSERT INTO artists VALUES(154,'The Weeknd',3,'https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6761610000f178b5f9e28219c169fd4b9e8379','https://open.spotify.com/artist/1Xyo4u8uXC1ZmMpatF05PJ','The Weeknd took over pop music & culture on his own terms filtering R&B, Pop,& hip-hop through an ambitious widescreen lens. The multi-platinum 4X GRAMMY Award winner has emerged as one of the most successful & significant artists of the modern era');
INSERT INTO artists VALUES(158,'Travis Scott',3,'https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6761610000f178e707b87e3f65997f6c09bfff','https://open.spotify.com/artist/0Y5tJX1MQlPlqiwlOH1tJY','Houston-born rapper and producer Travis Scott''s psychedelic trap style makes him one of the more distinctive talents to have risen to the height of mainstream commercial popularity. His heavily processed, half-sung/half-rapped style set him apart early on');
INSERT INTO artists VALUES(160,'Tyler The Creator',3,'https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6761610000f1788278b782cbb5a3963db88ada','https://open.spotify.com/artist/4V8LLVI7PbaPR0K2TGSxFF','Tyler, The Creator is a rapper and producer distinguished above all other singular qualities by his gravelly voice and an irascible disposition befitting a collision-shop owner. ');
INSERT INTO artists VALUES(161,'Vance Joy',3,'https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6761610000f1788f074ec8c25406680bf26422','https://open.spotify.com/artist/10exVja0key0uqUkk6LJRT','Australian indie folk singer/songwriter Vance Joy began his career playing the Melbourne open-mike scene at the end of the 2000s while completing his law degree. Finding success with his intimate Bon Iver-influenced songs, Joy decided to put law on hold and pursue a music career instead. ');
INSERT INTO artists VALUES(163,'XXXTENTACION',3,'https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6761610000f178f0c20db5ef6c6fbe5135d2e4','https://open.spotify.com/artist/15UsOTVnJzReFVN1VCnxy4','Controversial rapper Jahseh Dwayne Onfroy (aka XXXTentacion) played fast and loose when it came to genres, often incorporating elements of punk rock, hip-hop, R&B, and heavy metal. In the late 2010s, he experienced a quick rise with his dark and emotionally intense content, scoring a number one album with 2018''s ?. Months later, at the peak of his popularity, he was shot and killed.');
INSERT INTO artists VALUES(167,'Young Thug',3,'https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6761610000f178547d2b41c9f2c97318aad0ed','https://open.spotify.com/artist/50co4Is1HCEo8bhOyUWKpn','Flouting hip-hop conventions while defying gender and sexuality stereotypes, Young Thug has been one of the most distinctive contemporary rap artists since attaining his chart debut with Stoner (2014).');
INSERT INTO artists VALUES(168,'Zara Larsson',3,'https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6761610000f178a63a2b0ceb57eb509d67c90f','https://open.spotify.com/artist/1Xylc3o4UrD53lo9CvFvVg','Swedish hitmaking singer/songwriter Zara Larsson crafts R&B- and club-influenced dance-pop. After winning a Swedish singing competition at the age of eight, Larsson crashed the mainstream in the mid-2010s with a string of Swedish number ones.');
INSERT INTO artists VALUES(170,'ZAYN',3,'https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6761610000f1789fbf7133dfc04d4cd44ccd36','https://open.spotify.com/artist/5ZsFI1h6hIdQRw2ti0hz81','ZAYN is a multi-platinum selling recording artist, songwriter, producer, and philanthropist known for his skyscraping vocals and hybrid style of pop and R&B.');
